    experiment/phase-8a-snapshot-fix: fill bus.snapshot() balances + portfolios from WalletTool
    
    C-049 (Codex audit N-2): bus.snapshot() hardcoded empty HashMap for both
    balances and portfolios. Every agent prompt displayed `Balance: 0 Coins`
    even when wallet held funds → Art. II.2 economic signal falsified across
    all prior TAPE_ECONOMY / Hayek bounty / reward-pull experiments.
    
    Fix: enumerate from mounted WalletTool via `as_any().downcast_ref()`.
    Absent-wallet case preserved (returns empty, does not panic).
    
    Tests: tests/snapshot_nonempty.rs (4 tests, all green)
      - snapshot_balances_nonempty_after_genesis
      - snapshot_portfolio_appears_after_invest
      - snapshot_reflects_wallet_mutations
      - snapshot_empty_when_no_wallet_mounted
    
    Full test suite on branch: 116/118 pass. 2 pre-existing failures in
    reward_pull_conservation.rs exist on main too; unrelated to this change
    (to be handled in a separate Phase 8 sub-task).
    
    Refs: handover/audits/EXT_CODEX_2026-04-22.md (N-2)
          handover/ai-direct/PLAN_FINAL_PHASE_8_TO_PAPER_2026-04-22.md §4 Phase 8.A
    
